title: I'm Korean & Don't Relate To The K-Wave, But That's OK
text: Park Hae-Soo, Jung Ho-Yeon, and Lee Jung-Jae, the stars of @squidgame.The series continues to break records as the most watched program in Netflix history, and as the first Korean and non-English series nominated for Best Ensemble at the @sagawards. pic.twitter.com/F4ZdNftkaa
